<http://model.geneontology.org/R-HSA-157629_UniProt_O14672>
        a       <http://identifiers.org/uniprot/O14672> , <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> ;
        <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>
